		<item>
			<title>Citizens beyond walls summer workcamps: Peace weeks</title>
			<link>http://www.via.dds.nl/joomla2/index.php/citizens-beyond-walls/273-peace-weeks-for-cbw</link>
			<guid isPermaLink="true">http://www.via.dds.nl/joomla2/index.php/citizens-beyond-walls/273-peace-weeks-for-cbw</guid>
			<description><![CDATA[<div class="feed-description"><p><strong>As part of the project 8 special "Peace-Week" workcamp projects will be held in each of the participating 8 European countries in the summer of 2014: Greece, Spain, Serbia, Italy, Bulgaria, Hungary, The Netherlands, Germany</strong></p>
<p> </p>
<p><span style="font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small; line-height: 1.3em;">The aim of the project "Citizens Beyond Walls" is fostering inclusive policies to respect Citizens' rights in Europe, with specific focus on new citizens and minorities. Extreme right wing groups are a threat for peace in Europe, where peace is not only absence of conflict but the condition where citizens' are equally endowed of rights. "Citizens Beyond Walls", is an action aimed at activating European Citizens to counter the mentioned process. </span></p>
<p><strong style="line-height: 1.3em;"><span style="font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small; line-height: 1.3em;"> </span></strong></p>
<p><strong style="line-height: 1.3em;"><span style="font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small; line-height: 1.3em;">How to apply?</span></strong></p>
<p><span style="font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;"><span style="line-height: 16px;">If you are interested </span></span><span style="font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;"><span>you must look </span></span><span style="line-height: 1.3em; font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;">at </span><a href="http://www.workcamps.info" style="line-height: 16px; font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;">www.workcamps.info</a><span style="line-height: 1.3em;">, register your profile </span><span style="line-height: 16px; font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;">and type `</span><strong style="line-height: 16px; font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;">peace week´ </strong><span style="line-height: 16px; font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;">at the browser. Then you only have to fill your application and send it to us at <a href="mailto:outgoing@stichtingvia.nl">outgoing@stichtingvia.nl</a>. For the special peace-week workcamp, VIA will reimburse the volunteers travel costs to the peace week (maximum reimbursement for tickets can apply). The volunteers will have to pay the normal workcamp fee of 110 Euros in order to participate</span></p>
<p><span style="font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;"><span style="line-height: 16px;">Do not waste this opportunity to join this wonderful project!</span></span></p>
<p> </p>
<p><strong><span style="font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small; line-height: 1.3em;"> </span></strong></p></div>]]></description>
