			<description><![CDATA[<div class="feed-description"><p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;">VIA and the CBW team attended in Amsterdam the opening of <span style="line-height: 1.3em;">' The Rise of Populism', a great exhibition which </span></span><span style="font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;"><span style="line-height: 1.3em;">gives a versatile picture of the contemporary political and social landscape </span></span><span style="font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;"><span style="line-height: 1.3em;">in Europe and an insight into the </span></span><span style="line-height: 1.3em;">complexity of the concept of ' populism '.</span></span></p>
