			<title>Demonstration Against Racism</title>
			<link>http://www.via.dds.nl/joomla2/index.php/citizens-beyond-walls/264-demonstration-against-racism</link>
			<guid isPermaLink="true">http://www.via.dds.nl/joomla2/index.php/citizens-beyond-walls/264-demonstration-against-racism</guid>
			<description><![CDATA[<div class="feed-description"><p><span style="font-size: small; font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;">On March 22nd a large Demonstration Against Racism, organised by 'Comité 21 Maart', took place in Amsterdam. Thousands of people gathered at the Museumplein and marched to the Jonas Daniël Meijerplein, raising their voices against racism in The Netherlands. The CBW Team was also there, to support and to hand out short questionnaires to participants for our research."</span></p>
<hr class="system-pagebreak" />
